name: Nebraska football
summary: On Friday night, #24-ranked Illinois will face its first Big Ten Conference road test against #22-ranked Nebraska. According to the odds and predictions, Illinois is a slight underdog in the game. However, the Fighting Illini have a proven model for success against Nebraska, having won two of the last three meetings.

summary: On Saturday, September 16th, 2023, San Jose State will face off against Washington State in a college football game. name: Freddie Owens
summary: Freddie Owens, a South Carolina death row inmate, was executed by lethal injection on June 15, 2023. Owens had been convicted of murdering a convenience store clerk in 1998, and his execution was the first in the state in 13 years. The South Carolina Supreme Court rejected his claim that he did not kill the clerk, and an eleventh-hour witness statement change did not stop the execution. Letters written by Owens reveal his vulnerable and angry thoughts on death row.

summary: Several news articles report on the reopening of the Three Mile Island nuclear plant in Pennsylvania. The deal with Microsoft is part of a growing trend of businesses seeking clean energy sources for their operations. The plant's reopening will restore jobs to the area and contribute to the state's efforts to reduce carbon emissions. It is expected to begin providing power to Microsoft data centers in 2023.

name: Nebraska
summary: Several news articles focus on Senator Lindsey Graham's visit to Nebraska, where he advocated for a change in the state's electoral vote system. Nebraska currently awards two electoral votes to the winner of the statewide popular vote and one electoral vote to the winner of each congressional district. The proposed change would award all five electoral votes to the statewide winner, potentially benefiting Republican candidates. Graham's visit was supported by Governor Jim Pillen and former President Donald Trump. In other news, the University of Illinois Fighting Illini defeated the University of Nebraska Cornhuskers in a college football game, while the Nebraska Volleyball team defeated the Stanford Cardinal in a volleyball match. The Nebraska Panthers football team lost to the University of Northern Iowa Panthers, marking their first loss of the season.

name: Menendez brothers
summary: The Menendez brothers, Erik and Lyle, gained notoriety for the brutal murder of their wealthy parents in the 1980s. Their case has been the subject of much fascination and controversy. Dr. Jerome Oziel, their therapist, played a significant role in the investigation as he broke patient privilege to alert authorities. The Netflix series "Monsters Inside: The 24 Faces of Billy Milligan" delves into the events leading up to the murders and explores the brothers' motivations. Despite the series' strong performances, critics found the story to be lacking and ultimately unsatisfying. Questions remain about the brothers' current whereabouts and the possibility of their release from prison based on new evidence.
